WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.057
Myocarditis remains a diagnostic challenge with

00:00:03.057 --> 00:00:04.076
high-stakes consequences.

00:00:04.076 --> 00:00:07.133
In this clinical review, we examine

00:00:07.133 --> 00:00:10.190
the adverse effects every practitioner must

00:00:10.190 --> 00:00:10.700
anticipate.
